      "title": "Background",
      "text": "<style=Highlight>We recommend experiencing the [Ashes of Time] story before reading this Vassal Journal.</style>\n\n'Thousands of years, gone in the blink of an eye.'\n\nHer hood and veil cloaked her visage; none would know her true identity. Perhaps even she has forgotten.\n\nShould one defy destiny, or follow the path of fate?\n\nFor the one true future, within the annihilating void, a Vassal whom none remember endures her endless, futile vigil.",
